title: Iran 2009 election protest videos -- compilation 5
description:
A compilation of the 83 videos collected to date by Anonymous depicting the brutality with which the Iranian government is terrorizing protesters.

Many of these videos contain graphic images of violent death. Protesters have been attacked with guns, clubs and fists. If arrested, they face the possibility of being tortured to death.

The protesters against Ahmedinejad and Khameini have used a strategy of nonviolence. Almost all of the people you see being arrested, beaten and killed in these videos have done nothing more than carry a sign or shout a slogan.

The protesters are not fighting against Islam. They are not fighting for America or Britain or Israel. All they want is the free, peaceful, democratic Iran their parents and grandparents fought and died for.

If you want to help, join us at http://iran.whyweprotest.net/

The master list of Anonymous's Iran videos is located at http://gonzotimes.net/?page_id=500
